SMART CONTRACT CODE — SEPARATE OWNERSHIP
==============================================================================

The BGPC smart contract was deployed using Bitbond Token Tool, a no-code
token deployment platform operated by Bitbond GmbH (Berlin, Germany).

    Bitbond Token Tool:  https://tokentool.bitbond.com
    Operator:            Bitbond GmbH, Berlin, Germany

The underlying contract template "BitbondTokenToolAdvancedToken" is the
intellectual property of Bitbond GmbH, NOT of Golden Poysha.

If you wish to use, modify, fork, or reference the smart contract code:

